1574
02:04:04.120 --> 02:04:07.680
Meredith Logue. You were kissing
someone. It looked like Meredith.

1575
02:04:14.120 --> 02:04:17.480
I came out to find you.

1576
02:04:17.560 --> 02:04:19.880
Oh. hardly kissing.

1577
02:04:21.240 --> 02:04:24.240
