That could take me
some time.

1613
02:06:42.880 --> 02:06:46.600
Tom is talented.
Tom is tender.

1614
02:06:47.920 --> 02:06:49.840
Tom is beautiful.

1615
02:06:49.880 --> 02:06:52.240
You're such a liar.

1616
02:06:55.400 --> 02:06:58.640
Tom is--
Tom is a mystery.

1617
02:07:04.000 --> 02:07:06.440
Tom is not a nobody.

1618
02:07:09.920 --> 02:07:13.640
Tom has secrets
he doesn't want to tell me.

1619
02:07:13.680 --> 02:07:15.960
and I wish he would.

1620
02:07:19.960 --> 02:07:22.320
Tom has nightmares.

1621
02:07:26.200 --> 02:07:28.560
That's not a good thing.

1622
02:07:32.960 --> 02:07:35.440
Tom has someone to love him.

1623
02:07:36.960 --> 02:07:39.280
That is a good thing.

1624
02:07:42.000 --> 02:07:46.280
Mmm.
Tom is crushing me.

1625
02:07:46.360 --> 02:07:49.600
Tom is crushing me.

1626
02:07:49.680 --> 02:07:53.360
- Tom. Tom. you're crush--

1627
02:07:53.400 --> 02:07:56.200
- Oh. God!

1628
02:07:56.240 --> 02:07:58.040
Oh. God!

1629
02:07:58.120 --> 02:07:59.960
- Oh. God!

1630
02:08:06.840 --> 02:08:09.200
Oh. God! Peter.

1631
02:10:32.240 --> 02:10:34.600
You don't know

1632
