With a taste for tears

1649
02:11:54.880 --> 02:11:58.280
Soon lose their taste

1650
02:11:58.360 --> 02:12:01.880
For kissing

1651
02:12:03.560 --> 02:12:06.000
You don't know

1652
02:12:06.040 --> 02:12:09.400
How hearts burn

1653
02:12:11.160 --> 02:12:13.160
A love that cannot live

1654
